{
  "stem": "24195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I try to explain that I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I had learned the word for Jewish in-- for being Jewish-- for Jew in-- in Russian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I could say that, because then one of the older men in the basement of this house was a former White Russian, who had immigrated after World War I to Germany.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he had told me the words.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and he gets still-- later, he was still a little bit on-- on-- apprehensive when I told him and seemed to be angered.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then later, I found out that 'Jew' is a curse word in Russian, a lot of times.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like-- it's like calling somebody an SOB or something worse than that, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- but I-- somehow I calmed him down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't speak German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't speak Russian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he looked so young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I went-- I went over to the table.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said-- I tried to tell him how old-- find out how old he is and how old I am.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went over to the table.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had no pencil, no paper, but a big-- big layer of dust on the kitchen table.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I go and draw an 18 in there, and going like this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he points-- same age.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he's real friendly now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he pulls out tobacco and some-- some tobacco cigarette paper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he starts you know-- and offers me and he rolls a cigarette for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was-- So he didn't hurt you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was the beginning of a-- of a friend-- of a friendly relation-- you know, of a friendly reception there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, so I didn't have any-- any problem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were worse scenes.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
